steps.name: I am on the Home Page "https://www.carsguide.com.au" of CarsGuide Website
I move to Car For Sale Menu
click on "Search Cars" link
select carbrand as "BMW" from AnyMake dropdown
select "1 SERIES" as car model
select location as "Australia" from SelectLocation dropdown
select "$1,000" as price
click on Find_My_Next_Car button
I should see list of searched cars
